.TH SEATUYA 3 "2026-03-06" "seatuya 0.1.0" "Library Functions Manual"
.SH NAME
seatuya \- C wrapper for the tuyapp Tuya library
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B #include <seatuya/seatuya.h>
.PP
.BI "const char *seatuya_version(void);"
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B seatuya
provides a pure C API wrapping the tuyapp C++ library for
communicating with Tuya smart devices.
.PP
.BR seatuya_version ()
returns a string containing the library version.
.SH RETURN VALUES
.BR seatuya_version ()
returns a pointer to a static string. The caller must not free it.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR tuyapp (3)
